$ envtool set PORT 8080
Environment variable PORT set to 8080
$ envtool set API_KEY secret123
Environment variable API_KEY set to secret123

# List all allowed variables
$ envtool list
Allowed environment variables:
DATABASE_URL=unset
API_KEY=secret123
PORT=8080
